statements.sql: select "roles".*, "model_has_roles"."model_id" as "pivot_model_id", "model_has_roles"."role_id" as "pivot_role_id", "model_has_roles"."model_type" as "pivot_model_type" from "roles" inner join "model_has_roles" on "roles"."id" = "model_has_roles"."role_id" where "model_has_roles"."model_id" = 1 and "model_has_roles"."model_type" = 'App\Models\User'

select "roles".*, "model_has_roles"."model_id" as "pivot_model_id", "model_has_roles"."role_id" as "pivot_role_id", "model_has_roles"."model_type" as "pivot_model_type" from "roles" inner join "model_has_roles" on "roles"."id" = "model_has_roles"."role_id" where "model_has_roles"."model_id" in (1) and "model_has_roles"."model_type" = 'App\Models\User'

select exists(select * from "users" where exists (select * from "roles" inner join "model_has_roles" on "roles"."id" = "model_has_roles"."role_id" where "users"."id" = "model_has_roles"."model_id" and "model_has_roles"."model_type" = 'App\Models\User' and "name" = 'Developer') and "users"."id" = 1) as "exists"

select "users"."id", "users"."profileId", "project_users"."projectId" as "pivot_projectId", "project_users"."userId" as "pivot_userId" from "users" inner join "project_users" on "users"."id" = "project_users"."userId" where exists (select * from "roles" inner join "model_has_roles" on "roles"."id" = "model_has_roles"."role_id" where "users"."id" = "model_has_roles"."model_id" and "model_has_roles"."model_type" = 'App\Models\User' and "name" = 'Developer') and "project_users"."projectId" in (5)
select count(*) as aggregate from "attachments" where "attachments"."attachableType" = 'App\Models\Ticket' and "attachments"."attachableId" = 29 and "attachments"."attachableId" is not null

select "attachments".*, (select "id" from "attachments" as "a" where "attachments"."id" = "a"."id" limit 1) as "can-view", (select "id" from "attachments" as "a" where "attachments"."id" = "a"."id" limit 1) as "can-delete" from "attachments" where "attachments"."attachableType" = 'App\Models\Ticket' and "attachments"."attachableId" = 29 and "attachments"."attachableId" is not null order by "id" desc limit 10 offset 0
select count(*) as aggregate from "change_logs" where "change_logs"."changableType" = 'App\Models\Ticket' and "change_logs"."changableId" = 29 and "change_logs"."changableId" is not null

select "id", "date", (select (CASE
WHEN data->>'property' = 'Priority' THEN json_build_object('property', data->>'property', 'oldValue', (SELECT tp.name FROM ticket_priorities as tp WHERE id = (data->>'oldValue')::bigint), 'newValue', (SELECT tp.name FROM ticket_priorities as tp WHERE id = (data->>'newValue')::bigint))
WHEN data->>'property' = 'Type' THEN json_build_object('property', data->>'property', 'oldValue', (SELECT tt.name FROM ticket_types as tt WHERE id = (data->>'oldValue')::bigint), 'newValue', (SELECT tt.name FROM ticket_types as tt WHERE id = (data->>'newValue')::bigint))
WHEN data->>'property' = 'Assignee' THEN json_build_object('property', data->>'property', 'oldValue', (SELECT pr.name FROM profiles as pr WHERE id = (SELECT "profileId" FROM users WHERE id = (data->>'oldValue')::bigint)), 'newValue', (SELECT pr.name FROM profiles as pr WHERE id = (select "profileId" from users where id = (data->>'newValue')::bigint)))
ELSE data
END)) as "resolvedData", "change_logs"."changableId", "change_logs"."changableType", "change_logs"."initiatorId" from "change_logs" where "change_logs"."changableType" = 'App\Models\Ticket' and "change_logs"."changableId" = 29 and "change_logs"."changableId" is not null order by "id" desc limit 10 offset 0

select * from "users" where (exists (select * from "roles" inner join "model_has_roles" on "roles"."id" = "model_has_roles"."role_id" where "users"."id" = "model_has_roles"."model_id" and "model_has_roles"."model_type" = 'App\Models\User' and "name" = 'Admin') or exists (select * from "projects" inner join "project_users" on "projects"."id" = "project_users"."projectId" where "users"."id" = "project_users"."userId" and exists (select * from "tickets" where "projects"."id" = "tickets"."projectId" and "tickets"."id" = 29) and exists (select "id" from "users" where exists (select * from "roles" inner join "model_has_roles" on "roles"."id" = "model_has_roles"."role_id" where "users"."id" = "model_has_roles"."model_id" and "model_has_roles"."model_type" = 'App\Models\User' and "name" in ('Admin', 'Project Manager')) and "id" in (select "userId" from "project_users" where "projectId" = "projects"."id") and ("id" = "project_users"."userId") limit 1)) or exists (select * from "tickets" where "users"."id" = "tickets"."assigneeId" and "tickets"."id" = 29) or exists (select * from "tickets" where "users"."id" = "tickets"."creatorId" and "tickets"."id" = 29)) or (exists (select * from "roles" inner join "model_has_roles" on "roles"."id" = "model_has_roles"."role_id" where "users"."id" = "model_has_roles"."model_id" and "model_has_roles"."model_type" = 'App\Models\User' and "name" = 'Developer') and exists (select * from "projects" inner join "project_users" on "projects"."id" = "project_users"."projectId" where "users"."id" = "project_users"."userId" and exists (select * from "tickets" where "projects"."id" = "tickets"."projectId" and "tickets"."id" = 29)))
